data.meta_description: The Bend Bulletin (Bend, Oregon) 3 Dec 1947, Sat Page 5 Funeral Rites Held For John Helfrich Funeral services were held at 1 p.m. today at St. Francis of Assisi Catholic church for John Helfrich, who died Thursday a the St. Charles hospital.
